 19	 * `hotels`, projected by `toConference` from validated document `Option`s).
 20	 *
 21	 * These render-to-string tests pin the load-bearing claim of the extraction
 22	 * (`prove-it-works`): a fully-populated conference renders every section, and
 23	 * the data-driven sections render the boundary data — NOT the old hard-coded
